title: Receipts of Butter, Gross Weight for Boston, MA; Chicago, IL; San Francisco, CA; New York, NY; and Philadelphia, PA
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1912-1920 (2)--Original Data, 1918-1941. The Five Markets Covered By These Data Are Boston, Chicago, San Francisco, New York, And Philadelphia. The Gross Weight Includes Containers And Wrappers. Source: United States Department Of Agriculture, Annual Yearbooks Of Agriculture, And Agricultural Statistics.

This NBER data series m01070b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
